                                                  5</ref>)</enactingFormula><sourceNote>(Enacting provision omitted—<ref href="hk/2019/er6">E.R. 6 of 2019</ref>)</sourceNote><enactingFormula role="empoweringSection">
                                                <marker role="blank-line"></marker>
