                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <p>M.</p>
                        </td>
                        <td colspan="2">
                            <p>TOXINS</p>
                        </td>
                        <td></td>
                        <td></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td></td>
                        <td colspan="2">
                            <paragraph xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" name="1" temporalId="sch0_1" id="ID_1571369315052_019"><num class="align_right" value="1">(a)</num><content class="align_justified">Waste discharges shall not cause
                                    the toxins in water to attain such levels as to produce
                                    significant toxic, carcinogenic, mutagenic or teratogenic
                                    effects in humans or fish or any other aquatic organisms, with
                                    due regard to biologically cumulative effects in food chains and
                                    to toxicant interactions with each other.</content></paragraph>
                        </td>
